Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx_pause_pkt_dmac

AGL_GMX_TX_PAUSE_PKT_DMAC = Packet TX Pause Packet DMAC field

Notes: Additionally reset when both MIX0/1_CTL[RESET] are set to 1.
